      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it's just... it doesn't feel like life anymore. it's just like i'm a ghost living in a museum of things we used to have. i try to do stuff, like cook or clean, but it's all so gray. like there's no color left in anything. i just want everything to stop. the noise in my head, the emptiness... i just want it to be quiet for real.",
